name: TheParty Event Ticket #1 (NFT Artwork by FatBaby)
description: This ticket entitles the holder, or assignee, to one fully customized promotion/entertainment event with TheParty inside the Decentraland metaverse. Collectors can purchase the NFT and assign the event package as a gift to an NFT artist/project of their choice. They can choose to retain the NFT even if they choose to gift the services. Please contact TheParty at Twitter @DclPromoter or Discord TheParty#2820 for additional information.
